thread.title: Dexter Kho
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Dexter Kho

author: Dexter Kho
title: Dexter Kho
text:
This is the first time I used Pack and Send to delivery a parcel overseas. The online booking was easy to use. Managed to drop off the parcel at the service center without any issue. Great support from the staff there. Parcel reached the overseas destination 3 days from drop off date which exceeded my expectation.
Overall great service with competitive pricing!!!
